Governor Kayode Fayemi of Ekiti State has joined several other political leaders in the country to congratulate former Governor Ayodele Peter Fayose of Ekiti State who turned 60 years on Sunday.
Dr.  Fayemi in a statement conveyed the goodwill of the government and the people of Ekiti State to the former Ekiti State Governor. “The government and good people of Ekiti State, Land of Honour, rejoice with His Excellency, Chief Ayodele Peter Fayose, former governor of Ekiti State, as he turns 60 years old today, Sunday, November 15, 2020.
“It’s been sixty amazing years. We thank God for his blessings he has bestowed on you these past years and we pray He continues to bless and sustain you with good health,” the governor stated.
